'''山案座'''是靠近南[[天極|天極]]的[[南天_(天球)|南天]]小[[星座|星座]]，属法国天文学家[[尼可拉·路易·拉卡伊|尼可拉·路易·拉卡伊]]18世纪划分的14个星座。星座原名“{{lang|la|Mensa}}”是[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]，意为桌子，原指“{{lang|la|Mons Mensae}}”，即[[桌山|桌山]]。山案座属[[國際天文聯會|國際天文聯會]]指定的[[星座列表|88个现代星座]]，覆盖153.5[[平方度|平方度]]夜空排名第75。除南天极的[[南极座|南极座]]外，山案座是最靠南面的星座，北半球只有[[北纬5度线|北纬5度线]]以南才能观测。

山案座亮度在88个现代星座基本垫底，完全没有明亮恒星，最亮的[[山案座α|山案座α]]仅在理想天气的郊区夜空勉强可见。[[大麦哲伦星系|大麦哲伦星系]]众多[[星团|星团]]与[[类星体|类星体]]在山案座范围，至少三个恒星系发现[[太陽系外行星|系外行星]]。

== 历史 ==
法国天文学家[[尼可拉·路易·拉卡伊|尼可拉·路易·拉卡伊]]在[[好望角|好望角]]停留两年观察并分类上万颗[[南天_(天球)|南天]]恒星，在欧洲无法观测的[[南天_(天球)|南天]]星空划分14个星座，另外13个用象征[[啟蒙時代|啟蒙時代]]的科学仪器命名，仅代表[[桌山|桌山]]的山案座例外<ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|6–7}}。桌山是可俯瞰[[開普敦|開普敦]]的南非山峰，距拉卡伊观测星空的天文台不远。星座原名“{{lang|la|Mons Mensae}}”指桌山，据拉卡伊回忆，[[麥哲倫雲|麥哲倫雲]]又称开普云，东南方向刮来暴风雨时乌云经常笼罩桌山，就像“桌子”藏在云后的天上<ref name="Wagman-2003">{{cite book | last = Wagman | first = Morton | year = 2003 | title = Lost Stars: Lost, Missing and Troublesome Stars from the Catalogues of Johannes Bayer, Nicholas Louis de Lacaille, John Flamsteed, and Sundry Others | publisher = The McDonald & Woodward Publishing Company | location = Blacksburg, VA | isbn = 978-0939923786}}</ref>{{rp|207–208}}。1844年[[約翰·赫歇爾|約翰·赫歇爾]]提议把星座名称缩短成一个单词，毕竟拉卡伊命名星座后已将相当一部分名称缩短<ref>{{cite journal | author-link = 約翰·赫歇爾 | last = Herschel | first = John | year = 1844 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 6 | issue = 5 | pages = 60–62 | title = Farther Remarks on the Division of Southern Constellations | access-date = 2021-04-03 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=s-tBAQAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA62&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | doi = 10.1093/mnras/6.5.60a | archive-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220524204925/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=s-tBAQAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA62&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。

== 简介 ==
山案座北接[[劍魚座|劍魚座]]，西北和西侧靠[[水蛇座|水蛇座]]，南临[[南极座|南极座]]，东挨[[蝘蜓座|蝘蜓座]]，东北方向与[[飞鱼座|飞鱼座]]相邻，覆盖153.5平方度夜空，占0.372%，在[[星座列表|88个现代星座]]排第75<ref name="tirionconst">{{cite web | url = http://www.ianridpath.com/constellations2.html | title = Constellations: Lacerta–Vulpecula | work = Star Tales | last = Ridpath | first = Ian | publisher = self-published | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210312043308/http://www.ianridpath.com/constellations2.html | access-date = 2021-03-26 | archive-date = 2021-03-12 }}</ref>。1922年，[[國際天文聯會|国际天文联会]]确定以三字母缩写“{{lang|la|Men}}”代指山案座<ref name="pa30_469">{{cite journal | last = Russell | first = Henry Norris | author-link = 亨利·诺利斯·罗素 | title = The New International Symbols for the Constellations | journal = [[通俗天文學_(美國雜誌)|Popular Astronomy]] | volume = 30 | page = 469 | bibcode = 1922PA.....30..469R | year = 1922}}</ref>。比利时天文学家[[尤金·德爾波特|尤金·德爾波特]]1930年正式划分星座边界，山案座呈八条边组成的多边形（见文首信息框）。星座在[[赤道坐標系統|赤道坐標系統]]的[[赤经|赤经]]位于{{RA|03|12|55.9008}}至{{RA|07|36|51.5289}}范围，[[赤纬|赤纬]]在−69.75°到−85.26°之间<ref name="boundary">{{Cite journal | title = Mensa, Constellation Boundary | journal = The Constellations | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210328025838/https://www.iau.org/public/themes/constellations/#men | publisher = [[國際天文聯會|International Astronomical Union]] | url = https://www.iau.org/public/themes/constellations/#men | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-04-03 | archive-date = 2021-03-28}}</ref>。除南天极的南极座外，山案座是最靠南面的星座，仅[[北纬5度线|北纬5度线]]以南可看到完整星座<ref name="tirionconst" />{{refn|group="注"|技术上来说北纬5到[[北緯20度線|20度]]也能看到部分罗盘座，但只高于地平线几度的恒星无论通过何等手段都无法观测<ref name="tirionconst" />。}}。

== 显著特点 ==

=== 恒星 ===
{{see also|山案座恒星列表}}
拉卡伊用[[拜耳命名法|拜耳命名法]]为星座分配α至λ共十个[[希腊字母|希腊字母]]（κ除外），[[本杰明·阿普索普·古尔德|本杰明·阿普索普·古尔德]]后来增加κ、μ、ν、ξ和π。通常这么黯淡的恒星没有资格以希腊字母命名，但古尔德觉得它们离南天极很近，有必要命名。<ref name="Wagman-2003" />{{rp|207–208}}88个现代星座仅山案座没有恒星亮度超过5.0[[视星等|视星等]]<ref name="arnold">{{cite book | last1 = Arnold | first1 = H.J.P | last2 = Doherty | first2 = Paul | last3 = Moore | first3 = Patrick | title = The Photographic Atlas of the Stars | publisher = CRC Press | location = Boca Raton, Florida | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=YjcvJUfnWBAC&pg=PA57&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | year = 1999 | page = 57 | isbn = 978-0750306546 | access-date = 2021-04-04 | archive-date = 2021-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210916200823/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=YjcvJUfnWBAC&pg=PA57&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>，最亮的[[山案座α|山案座α]]只有5.09视星等，仅在理想天气的郊区夜空勉强可见<ref name="simbad_a">{{cite web | url = http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-basic?Ident=alpha+mensae&submit=SIMBAD+search | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200915230354/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-basic?Ident=alpha+mensae&submit=SIMBAD+search | title = LTT 2490 – High proper-motion star | work = SIMBAD | publisher = [[斯特拉斯堡天文資料中心|Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg]] | access-date = 2021-04-04 | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-09-15}}</ref>，星座内共22颗恒星亮度不低于6.5视星等{{refn|group="注"|6.5视星等是肉眼在城乡结合位置理想夜空条件下能看到的光线最微弱天体<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Sky Publishing Corporation | access-date = 2019-04-08 | url = http://www.skyandtelescope.com/resources/darksky/3304011.html?page=1&c=y | title = The Bortle Dark-Sky Scale | last = Bortle | date = 2001-02 | work = [[天空與望遠鏡雜誌|Sky & Telescope]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190408163545/https://www.skyandtelescope.com/astronomy-resources/light-pollution-and-astronomy-the-bortle-dark-sky-scale/ | first = John E. | archive-date = 2019-04-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。}}<ref name="tirionconst" />。

山案座α是光谱等级G7V、离地33.32±0.02[[光年|光年]]的[[類太陽恆星|類太陽恆星]]<ref name="dr2">{{Cite DR2}}</ref>。25万年前该星离地不到11光年而且要明亮得多，接近2.0视星等<ref>{{cite web | first = Jim | last = Kaler | url = http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/alphamen.html | title = Alpha Mensae | work = Stars | publisher = [[伊利诺伊大学厄巴纳-香槟分校|University of Illinois]] | access-date = 2021-04-04 | archive-date = 2020-07-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200725035234/http://stars.astro.illinois.edu/sow/alphamen.html}}</ref>。山案座α周围[[紅外過量|紅外過量]]，表明附近有半径超过147[[天文單位|天文單位]]的[[星周盤|星周盤]]，估计星周盘温度低于2.2万[[开尔文|开尔文]]<ref name="aa555_A11">{{cite journal | last1 = Eiroa | first1 = C. | last2 = Marshall | first2 = J.P. | last3 = Mora | first3 = A. | last4 = Montesinos | first4 = B. | last5 = Absil | first5 = O. | last6 = Augereau | first6 = J.Ch. | last7 = Bayo | first7 = A. | last8 = Bryden | first8 = G. | last9 = Danchi | first9 = W. | last10 = del Burgo | first10 = C. | last11 = Ertel | first11 = S. | last12 = Fridlund | first12 = M. | last13 = Heras | first13 = A.M. | last14 = Krivov | first14 = A.V. | last15 = Launhardt | first15 = R. | last16 = Liseau | first16 = R. | last17 = Löhne | first17 = T. | last18 = Maldonado | first18 = J. | last19 = Pilbratt | first19 = G.L. | last20 = Roberge | first20 = A. | last21 = Rodmann | first21 = J. | last22 = Sanz-Forcada | first22 = J. | last23 = Solano | first23 = E. | last24 = Stapelfeldt | first24 = K. | last25 = Thébault | first25 = P. | last26 = Wolf | first26 = S. | last27 = Ardila | first27 = D. | last28 = Arévalo | first28 = M. | last29 = Beichmann | first29 = C. | last30 = Faramaz | first30 = V. | last31 = González-García | first31 = B.M. | last32 = Gutiérrez | first32 = R. | last33 = Lebreton | first33 = J. | last34 = Martínez-Arnáiz | first34 = R. | last35 = Meeus | first35 = G. | last36 = Montes | first36 = D. | last37 = Olofsson | first37 = G. | last38 = Su | first38 = K.Y.L. | last39 = White | first39 = G.J. | last40 = Barrado | first40 = D. | last41 