/sim-id?Ident=HD%2043834B | title = HD 43834B – Star | work = SIMBAD | publisher = Centre de Données astronomiques de Strasbourg | access-date = 2021-04-04 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200915215158/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=HD%2043834B | archive-date = 2020-09-15}}</ref>。

5.19视星等的[[山案座γ|山案座γ]]是星座第二亮恒星<ref name="bagnall" />，距地球104.9±0.5光年<ref name="dr2" />，已有约106亿年历史，以1.04倍[[太阳质量|太阳质量]]膨胀到五倍[[太阳半径|太阳半径]]<ref name="Wittenmyer2016">{{cite journal | title = The Pan-Pacific Planet Search. V. Fundamental Parameters for 164 Evolved Stars | last1 = Wittenmyer | first1 = Robert A. | last2 = Liu | first2 = Fan | last3 = Wang | first3 = Liang | last4 = Casagrande | first4 = Luca | last5 = Johnson | first5 = John Asher | last6 = Tinney | first6 = C.G. | display-authors = 3 | journal = The Astronomical Journal | volume = 152 | issue = 1 | id = 19 | page = 15 | year = 2016 | bibcode = 2016AJ....152...19W | arxiv = 1605.00323 | doi = 10.3847/0004-6256/152/1/19}}</ref>，是光谱等级K2III的橙巨星<ref name="Gray2006">{{cite journal | last1 = Gray | first1 = R.O. | last2 = Corbally | first2 = C.J. | last3 = Garrison | first3 = R.F. | last4 = McFadden | first4 = M.T. | last5 = Bubar | first5 = E.J. | last6 = McGahee | first6 = C.E. | last7 = O'Donoghue | first7 = A.A. | last8 = Knox | first8 = E.R. | display-authors = 3 | title = Contributions to the Nearby Stars (NStars) Project: spectroscopy of stars earlier than M0 within 40 pc-The Southern Sample | journal = [[天文期刊|The Astronomical Journal]] | volume = 132 | issue = 1 | pages = 161–170 | year = 2006 | bibcode = 2006AJ....132..161G | arxiv = astro-ph/0603770 | doi = 10.1086/504637}}</ref>。5.31视星等的[[山案座β|山案座β]]离地660±10光年<ref name="bagnall" /><ref name="dr2" />，是光谱等级G8III的黄巨星，质量约太阳3.6倍并有513倍[[太陽光度|太陽光度]]。该星已有2.7亿年历史，<ref name="Luck2015">{{cite journal | title = Abundances in the Local Region. I. G and K Giants | last1 = Luck | first1 = R. Earle | journal = The Astronomical Journal | volume = 150 | issue = 3 | id = 88 | page = 23 | year = 2015 | bibcode = 2015AJ....150...88L | doi = 10.1088/0004-6256/150/3/88 | arxiv = 1507.01466}}</ref>位于[[大麦哲伦星系|大麦哲伦星系]]前方<ref name="bagnall">{{cite book | last = Bagnall | first = Philip M. | title = The Star Atlas Companion: What You Need to Know about the Constellations | publisher = Springer | location = New York | year = 2012 | isbn = 978-1461408307 | page = 290 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=KcIg02TKW6QC&pg=PA290&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2021-04-04 | archive-date = 2022-05-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220504130420/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=KcIg02TKW6QC&pg=PA290&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。

[[山案座ζ|山案座ζ]]与[[山案座η|山案座η]]都有红外过量，表明周边存在星周盘<ref name="Ishihara2017">{{cite journal | title = Faint warm debris disks around nearby bright stars explored by AKARI and IRSF | last1 = Ishihara | first1 = Daisuke | last2 = Takeuchi | first2 = Nami | last3 = Kobayashi | first3 = Hiroshi | last4 = Nagayama | first4 = Takahiro | last5 = Kaneda | first5 = Hidehiro | last6 = Inutsuka | first6 = Shu-ichiro | last7 = Fujiwara | first7 = Hideaki | last8 = Onaka | first8 = Takashi | display-authors = 3 | journal = Astronomy & Astrophysics | volume = 601 | id = A72 | page = 18 | year = 2017 | bibcode = 2017A&A...601A..72I | arxiv = 1608.04480 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201526215}}</ref><ref name="Kim2001"/>。山案座ζ是光谱等级A5 III的衰老白巨星，距地球394±4光年<ref name="belle2012">{{cite journal | title = Interferometric observations of rapidly rotating stars | last1 = Belle | first1 = Gerard T. | journal = The Astronomy and Astrophysics Review | volume = 20 | issue = 1 | page = 51 | year = 2012 | bibcode = 2012A&ARv..20...51V | arxiv = 1204.2572 | doi = 10.1007/s00159-012-0051-2}}</ref><ref name="dr2" />。山案座η是光谱等级K4 III的橙巨星<ref name="Kim2001">{{cite journal | last1 = Kim | first1 = Sungsoo S. | last2 = Zuckerman | first2 = B. | last3 = Silverstone | first3 = Murray | title = Extent of Excess Far-Infrared Emission around Luminosity Class III Stars | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 550 | issue = 2 | pages = 1000–1006 | year = 2001 | bibcode = 2001ApJ...550.1000K | arxiv = astro-ph/0012001 | doi = 10.1086/319803}}</ref>，离地650±10光年<ref name="dr2" />。

光谱等级G1的[[山案座π|山案座π]]也是类太阳恒星，距地球59.62±0.07光年<ref name="dr2" />。2001年，科学家发现该星还有[[軌道離心率|离心]][[轨道_(力学)|轨道]][[亚恒星|亚恒星]]相伴<ref>{{cite journal | last = Jones | first = H.R.A. | title = A probable planetary companion to HD 39091 from Anglo-Australian Planet Search | journal = [[皇家天文學會月報|Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]] | volume = 333 | year = 2002 | pages = 871–875 | doi = 10.1046/j.1365-8711.2002.05459.x | last2 = Paul Butler | first2 = R. | last3 = Tinney | first3 = C.G. | last4 = Marcy | first4 = Geoffrey W. | last5 = Penny | first5 = Alan J. | last6 = McCarthy | first6 = Chris | last7 = Carter | first7 = Brad D. | last8 = Pourbaix | first8 = Dimitri | display-authors = 3 | arxiv = astro-ph/0112084 | bibcode = 2002MNRAS.333..871J | issue = 4}} ([https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0112084 在线版] {{Wayback|url=https://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0112084 |date=20200803225753 }})</ref>。结合更加精确的[[依巴谷卫星|依巴谷卫星]]数据判断，伴星在10.27至29.9倍[[木星質量|木星質量]]范围，这与亚恒星定义相符，如果再大就要归入[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]范围<ref name="ReffertQuirrenbach">{{cite journal | last1 = Reffert | first1 = S. | last2 = Quirrenbach | first2 = A. | title = Mass constraints on substellar companion candidates from the re-reduced Hipparcos intermediate astrometric data: nine confirmed planets and two confirmed brown dwarfs | year = 2011 | journal = Astronomy & Astrophysics | volume = 527 | at = id.A140 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201015861 | bibcode = 2011A&A...527A.140R | arxiv = 1101.2227}}</ref>。2018年9月16日，科学家公布发现山案座π第二颗亚恒星伴星的消息，这颗[[超级地球|超级地球]]的轨道周期为6.27天，是科学家通过[[凌日系外行星巡天衛星|凌日系外行星巡天衛星]]发现后公布的第一颗系外行星<ref name="Huang">{{cite journal | last1 = Huang | first1 = Chelsea Xu | last2 = Burt | first2 = Jennifer | first3 = Andrew | last3 = Vanderburg | first4 = Maximilian N. | last4 = Günther | first5 = Avi | last5 = Shporer | first6 = Jason A. | last6 = Dittmann | first7 = Joshua N.| last7 = Winn | first8 = Rob | last8 = Wittenmyer | first9 = Lizhou | last9 = Sha | first10 = Stephen R. | last10 = Kane | first11 = George R. | last11 = Ricker | first12 = Roland | last12 = Vanderspek | first13 = David W. | last13 = Latham | first14 = Sara | last14 = Seager | first15 = Jon | last15 = Jenkins | first16 = Douglas A. | last16 = Caldwell | first17 = Karen A. | last17 = Collins | first18 = Natalia | last18 = Guerrero | first19 = Jeffrey C. | last19 = Smith | first20 = Sam | last20 = Quinn | first21 = Stéphane | last21 = Udry | first22 = Francesco | last22 = Pepe | first23 = François | last23 = Bouchy | first24 = Damien | last24 = Sé gransan | first25 = Christophe | last25 = Lovis | first26 = David | last26 = Ehrenreich | first27 = Maxime | last27 = Marmier | first28 = Michel | last28 = Mayor | first29 = Bill | last29 = Wohler | first30 = Kari | last30 = Haworth | first31 = Edward | last31 = Morgan | first32 = Michael | last32 = Fausnaugh | first33 = David | last33 = Charbonneau | first34 = Norio | last34 = Narita | year = 2018 | title = TESS Discovery of a Transiting Super-Earth in the Π Mensae System | journal = The Astrophysical Journal Letters | volume = 868 | issue = 2 | page = L39 | arxiv = 1809.05967 | doi = 10.3847/2041-8213/aaef91 | pmid = 31360431 | pmc = 6662726 | bibcode = 2018ApJ...868L..39H }}</ref>。

HD 38283是光谱等级F9.5V的类太阳恒星<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.nameexoworlds.iau.org/australia | title = Australia | website = NameExoworlds | access-date = 2021-04-04 | archive-date = 2020-12-05 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201205212545/http://www.nameexoworlds.iau.org/australia}}</ref>，亮度6.7视星等<ref name="tinney" />，离地124.3±0.1光年<ref name="dr2" />。2011年，科学家用[[都卜勒光譜學|径向速度法]]发现该星存在[[轨道周期|轨道周期]]363天（接近地球）的[[氣態巨行星|氣態巨行星]]，[[質量下限|質量下限]]约为木星三分之一<ref name="tinney">{{cite journal | last1 = Tinney | first1 = C.G. | first2 = Robert A. | last2 = Wittenmyer | first3 = R. Paul | last3 = Butler | first4 = Hugh R.A. | last4 = Jones | first5 = Simon J. | last5 = O'Toole | first6 = Jeremy A. | last6 = Bailey | first7 = Brad D. | last7 = Carter | first8 = J. | last8 = Horner | title = The Anglo-Australian Planet Search. XXI. A Gas-giant Planet in a One Year Orbit and the Habitability of Gas-giant Satellites | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | year = 2011 | volume = 732 | issue = 1 | pages = 31 | doi = 10.1088/0004-637x/732/1/31 | bibcode = 2011ApJ...732...31T | url = https://eprints.usq.edu.au/20482/3/Tinney_Wittenmyer_Butler_etal_AJ_2011_PV.pdf | dead-url = no | archive-url =  https://web.archive.org/web/20200314071849/https://eprints.usq.edu.au/20482/3/Tinney_Wittenmyer_Butler_etal_AJ_2011_PV.pdf | access-date = 2020-03-14 | format = PDF | archive-date = 2020-03-14}}</ref>。HD 39194是光谱等级K0V、8.08视星等的橙矮星，距地球86.21±0.09光年<ref name="dr2" />。[[高精度徑向速度行星搜索器|高精度徑向速度行星搜索器]]在附近发现三颗行星，公转周期分别是5.6、14和34天，质量下限分别是地球3.72、5.94和5.14倍<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Brandão | first1 = I.M. | title = The HARPS search for southern extra-solar planets XXXIV. Occurrence, mass distribution and orbital properties of super-Earths and Neptune-mass planets | last2 = Dogan | first2 = G. | last3 = Christensen-Dalsgaard | first3 = J. | last4 = Cunha | first4 = M.S. | last5 = Bedding | first5 = T.R. | last6 = Metcalfe | first6 = T.S. | last7 = Kjeldsen | first7 = H. | last8 = Bruntt | first8 = H. | last9 = Arentoft | first9 = T. | year= 2011 | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | bibcode = 2011arXiv1109.2497M | arxiv = 1109.2497}}</ref>。

山案座TZ是亮度以8.57天周期在6.2到6.9范围变化的[[食雙星|食雙星]]<ref name="arnold" />，由两颗距离很近的[[A型主序星|白主序星]]组成。其中一颗光谱等级A0V，半径为太阳两倍，质量2.5倍；另一颗光谱等级A8V，半径是太阳1.4倍，质量1.5倍<ref>{{cite journal | title = The Surface Brightness-color Relations Based on Eclipsing Binary Stars: Toward Precision Better than 1% in Angular Diameter Predictions | last1 = Graczyk | first1 = Dariusz | last2 = Konorski | first2 = Piotr | last3 = Pietrzyński | first3 = Grzegorz | last4 = Gieren | first4 = Wolfgang | last5 = Storm | first5 = Jesper | last6 = Nardetto | first6 = Nicolas | last7 = Gallenne | first7 = Alexandre | last8 = Maxted, Pierre F.L. | last9 = Kervella | first9 = Pierre | last10= Kołaczkowski | first10 = Zbigniew | display-authors = 3 | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 837 | issue = 1 | id = 7 | page = 19 | year = 2017 | bibcode = 2017ApJ...837....7G | arxiv = 1611.09976 | doi = 10.3847/1538-4357/aa5d56}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | title = Absolute dimensions of eclipsing binaries. XII – TZ Mensae | last1 = Andersen | first1 = J. | last2 = Clausen | first2 = J.V. | last3 = Nordstrom | first3 = B. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 175 | issue = 1–2 | year = 1987 | pages = 60–70 | bibcode = 1987A&A...175...60A}}</ref>。山案座UX也是食双星，由两颗质量约太阳1.2倍且有22±5亿年历史的恒星组成<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Higl | first1 = J. | last2 = Weiss | first2 = A. | title = Testing stellar evolution models with detached eclipsing binaries | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | year = 2017 | volume = 608 | page = A62 | bibcode = 2017A&A...608A..62H | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201731008}}</ref>，以4.19天周期围绕彼此旋转<ref>{{cite journal | title = Absolute dimensions of eclipsing binaries. XIV – UX Mensae | last1 = Andersen | first1 = J. | last2 = Clausen | first2 = J.V. | last3 =  Magain | first3 =  P. | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 211 | issue = 2 | year = 1989 | pages = 346–352 | bibcode = 1989A&A...211..346A}}</ref>，离地338.2±0.9光年<ref name="dr2" />。山案座TY既是食双星，又是[[大熊座W型變星|大熊座W型變星]]，两星距离太近以至共用外围恒星材料。经过计算，两星中比较大的拥有1.86倍太阳质量，直径1.85倍，光度13.6倍；另一颗四成太阳质量，直径八成四，光度1.7倍；两星表面温度分别是8164和7183开尔文。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Maceroni | first1 = C. | last2 = van't Veer | first2 = F. | title = The properties of W Ursae Majoris contact binaries: new results and old problems. | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astronomy-and-astrophysics_1996-07_311_2/page/523 | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | year = 1996 | volume = 311 | pages = 523–531 | bibcode = 1996A&A...311..523M}}</ref>山案座YY是光谱等级K1III的橙巨星，约2.2倍太阳质量，直径12.7倍，光度70倍。该星以9.5天为周期高速旋转，发射的X射线极强，达到[[變星|后髮座FK型变星]]水平<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Audard | first1 = Marc | last2 = Telleschi | first2 = Alessandra | last3 = Güdel | first3 = Manuel | last4 = Skinner | first4 = Stephen L. | last5 = Pallavicini | first5 = Roberto | last6 = Mitra-Kraev | first6 = Urmila | title = Some like it hot: the X-ray emission of the giant star YY Mensae | journal = Astrophys. J. | year = 2004 | volume = 617 | issue = 1 | pages = 531–550 | bibcode = 2004ApJ...617..531A | doi = 10.1086/424590 | arxiv = astro-ph/0408345}}</ref>。这类变星估计是由恒星系接触后两颗恒星合并而成<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Howell | first1 = Steve B. | last2 = Mason | first2 =  Elena | last3 = Boyd | first3 = Patricia | last4 = Smith | first4 = Krista Lynne | last5 = Gelino | first5 = Dawn M. | title = Rapidly Rotating, X-Ray Bright Stars in the Kepler Field | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | year = 2016 | volume = 831 | issue = 1 | page = 27 |  bibcode = 2016ApJ...831...27H | doi = 10.3847/0004-637X/831/1/27 | arxiv = 1608.07828}}</ref>。山案座YY亮度8.05视星等，距地球707±6光年<ref name="dr2" />。山案座AH是[[激變變星|激變變星]]系，由围绕彼此以2小时57分轨道周期高速旋转的白矮星和红矮星组成。两星距离太近，白矮星从红矮星吸收物质形成按周期爆发导致星系突然变亮的[[吸积盘|吸积盘]]<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Gänsicke | first1 = B.T. | last2 = Koester | first2 = D. | title = SW Ursae Majoris, CU Velorum and AH Mensae: three more accreting white dwarfs unveiled? | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | year = 1999 | volume = 346 | pages = 151–157 | bibcode = 1999A&A...346..151G}}</ref>。[[山案座TU|山案座TU]]也是白矮星和红矮星组成的激变变星，以2小时49分公转周期围绕彼此旋转，[[超峰|超峰]]时间（即周期爆发后变亮的时间）在已发现的激变变星系名列前茅。通常激变变星爆发后的增亮周期是第37天增亮一天，超峰可在每194天增亮5到20天。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Sion | first1 = Edward M. | last2 = Gänsicke | first2 = Boris T. | last3 = Long | first3 = Knox S. | last4 = Szkody | first4 = Paula | last5 = Knigge | first5 = Christian | last6 = Hubeny | first6 = Ivan | last7 = deMartino | first7 = Domitilla | last8 = Godon | first8 = Patrick | title = Hubble Space Telescope STIS Spectroscopy of Long-Period Dwarf Novae in Quiescence | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | year = 2008 | volume = 681 | issue = 1 | pages = 543–553 | doi = 10.1086/586699 | bibcode = 2008ApJ...681..543S | arxiv = 0801.4703}}</ref>
