[[山案座AO|山案座AO]]是9.8视星等的黯淡[[橙矮星|橙矮星]]，质量和尺寸均为太阳八成<ref name="raceoc">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/200913644 | bibcode = 2010A&A...520A..15M | arxiv = 1004.1959 | title = RACE-OC project: Rotation and variability of young stellar associations within 100 pc | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 520 | page = A15 | year = 2010 | last1 = Messina | first1 = S | last2 = Desidera | first2 = S- | last3 = Turatto | first3 = M. | last4 = Lanzafame | first4 = A.C. | last5 = Guinan | first5 = E.F.}}</ref>，同时还是[[天龍座BY型變星|天龍座BY型變星]]<ref name="gcvs">{{cite journal | bibcode = 2009yCat....102025S | title = VizieR Online Data Catalog: General Catalogue of Variable Stars (Samus+ 2007–2013) | journal = VizieR On-line Data Catalog: B/GCVS. Originally Published in: 2009yCat....102025S | volume = 1 | display-authors = etal | last1 = Samus | first1 = N.N. | last2 = Durlevich | first2 = O.V. | year = 2009}}</ref>。这类星体的[[星斑|星斑]]非常明显， 以至自转时亮度都会变化<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126042902/http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/afoev/var/eby.htx | archive-date = 2021-01-26 | url = http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/afoev/var/eby.htx | title = BY Draconis variables | year = 2011 | access-date = 2021-04-04 | author = AFOEV | publisher = Observatoire de Strasbourg | dead-url = no}}</ref>。山案座AO是[[繪架座β移動星群|繪架座β移動星群]]成员，该星群正经过银河系，其中恒星大都很年轻，相互没有密切联系<ref name="raceoc" />。

[[WISE_0535-7500|WISE 0535-7500]]是两颗[[次棕矮星|次棕矮星]]组成的[[聯星系統|聯星系統]]，距地球47±3光年，光谱等级低于Y1，目前科技手段还无法分开观测。估计两星质量都在8到20倍木星范围，间隔不到一天文单位<ref name="Leggett2017">{{cite journal | title = The Y-type Brown Dwarfs: Estimates of Mass and Age from New Astrometry, Homogenized Photometry, and Near-infrared Spectroscopy | last1 = Leggett | first1 = S.K. | last2 = Tremblin | first2 = P. | last3 = Esplin | first3 = T.L. | last4 = Luhman | first4 = K.L. | last5 = Morley | first5 = Caroline V. | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 842 | issue = 2 | at = 118 | year = 2017 | arxiv = 1704.03573 | bibcode = 2017ApJ...842..118L | doi = 10.3847/1538-4357/aa6fb5}}</ref>。

