[[大麦哲伦星系|大麦哲伦星系]]少部分在山案座范围<ref>{{cite book | last1 = Tirion | first1 = Wil | last2 = Rappaport | first2 = Barry | last3 = Remaklus | first3 = Will | title = Uranometria 2000.0 | year = 2012 | edition = All Sky | publisher = Willmann-Bell | page = Chart 212 | no-pp = yes | isbn = 978-0943396972}}</ref>，大部分在相邻的劍魚座<ref name="arnold" />，是银河系的[[衛星星系|衛星星系]]，距地球16.3万公里<ref name="Nature">{{cite journal | last1 = Pietrzyński | first1 = G | first2 = D. | last2 = Graczyk | first3 = W. | last3 = Gieren | first4 = I.B. | last4 = Thompson | first5 = B. | last5 = Pilecki | first6 = A. | last6 = Udalski | first7 = I. | last7 = Soszyński | display-authors = 3 | title = An eclipsing-binary distance to the Large Magellanic Cloud accurate to two per cent | journal = Nature | year = 2013 | volume = 495 | issue = 7439 | pages = 76–79 | doi = 10.1038/nature11878 | pmid = 23467166 | arxiv = 1303.2063 | bibcode = 2013Natur.495...76P}}</ref>。其中位于山案座的恒星包括：[[山案座W|山案座W]]是黄白[[超巨星|超巨星]]，也是罕见的[[北冕座R型變星|北冕座R型變星]]<ref name="milone">{{cite journal | bibcode = 1990Ap&SS.172..263M | title = Identification charts for southern R Coronae Borealis-stars | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_astrophysics-and-space-science_1990-10_172_2/page/263 | journal = Astrophysics and Space Science | volume = 172 | issue = 2 | pages = 263 | last1 = Milone | first1 = Luis A. | year = 1990 | doi = 10.1007/BF00643318 | doi-broken-date = 2021-01-10}}</ref>；[[HDE_268835|HDE 268835]]是蓝色[[特超巨星|特超巨星]]，周围是巨大的星周盘<ref name="kastneretal">{{Cite journal | last1 = Kastner | first1 = J.H. | last2 = Buchanan | first2 = C.L. | last3 = Sargent | first3 = B. | last4 = Forrest | first4 = W.J. | title = SpitzerSpectroscopy of Dusty Disks around B\e] Hypergiants in the Large Magellanic Cloud | doi = 10.1086/500804 | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 638 | issue = 1 | page = L29 | year = 2006 |bibcode = 2006ApJ...638L..29K}}</ref>；[[R71|R71]]是[[高光度藍變星|高光度藍變星]]，2012年光度高峰达太阳上百万倍<ref name="mehner">{{cite journal | bibcode = 2017A&A...608A.124M | title = Spectroscopic and photometric oscillatory envelope variability during the S Doradus outburst of the luminous blue variable R71 | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | volume = 608 | page = A124 | last1 = Mehner | first1 = A. | last2 = Baade | first2 = D. | last3 = Groh | first3 = J.H. | last4 = Rivinius | first4 = T. | last5 = Hambsch | first5 = F.-J. | last6 = Bartlett | first6 = E.S. | last7 = Asmus | first7 = D. | last8 = Agliozzo | first8 = C. | last9 = Szeifert | first9 = T. | last10 = Stahl | first10 = O. | year = 2017 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/201731829 | arxiv = 1709.00160}}</ref>。NGC 1987是大麦哲伦星系的[[球狀星團|球狀星團]]，估计约有六亿年历史，包含大量衰老的红色恒星<ref>{{cite book | chapter-url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=F4lsaf2TTh4C&pg=PA229&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | chapter = Infrared Imaging of Intermediate Age LMC/SMC Clusters | title = The Magellanic Clouds: Proceedings of the 148th Symposium of the International Astronomical Union, held in Sydney, Australia, July 9–13, 1990 | publisher = Springer Science & Business Media | location = New York | editor1-last = Haynes | editor1-first = Raymond | editor2-last = Milne | editor2-first = Douglas | isbn = 978-0792311102 | first1 = H. | last1 = Zinnecker | first2 = F. | last2 = Ferraro | first3 = F. | last3 = Fusi Pecci | first4 = Alvio | last4 = Renzini | first5 = R. | last5 = Buonanno | first6 = C.E. | last6 = Corsi | first7 = D.M. | last7 = Turndrup | pages = 228–230 | date = 1991-02-28 | access-date = 2021-04-04 | archive-date = 2022-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220524204919/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=F4lsaf2TTh4C&pg=PA229&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>；NGC 1848是形成2700万年的[[疏散星团|疏散星团]]<ref>{{Cite journal | title = Determination of Reddening and Age for Ten Large Magellanic Cloud Star Clusters from Integrated Spectroscopy | last1 = Ahumada | first1 = Andrea V. | last2 = Vega | first2 = Luis R. | last3 = Clariá | first3 = Juan J. | last4 = Oddone | first4 = Mónica A.| last5 = Palma | first5 = Tali | display-authors = 3 | journal = Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific | volume = 128 | issue = 967 | page = 094101 | year = 2016 | bibcode = 2016PASP..128i4101A | arxiv = 1603.08840 | doi = 10.1088/1538-3873/128/967/094101}}</ref>。此外，山案座还有许多疏散星团，但绝大部分只能用大型望远镜观测<ref>{{cite book | last = Inglis | first = Mike | title = Observer's Guide to Star Clusters | publisher = Springer Science & Business Media | location = New York | year = 2013 | page = 148 | isbn = 978-1461475675 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=ewHABAAAQBAJ&pg=PA148&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false | access-date = 2021-04-04 | archive-date = 2022-05-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220504130428/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=ewHABAAAQBAJ&pg=PA148&redir_esc=y&hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cndr#v=onepage&q&f=false }}</ref>。

